          },
          {
            "text": "§7Merci !",
            "value": "quit",
            "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('goodbye');"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ability",
      "speaker": "veteran",
      "lines": [
        "§6Les Talents§r (Abilities) sont très importants !",
